These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: mystery, scientific, comedy, animation, martial-arts
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: salsa, reggae, rock, punk, techno
1. the fan of punk is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of rock##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
5. the fan of techno is on the far left##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is in the middle##1
7. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | comedy | mystery | martial-arts | animation |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | salsa | rock     | punk       | reggae  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, hot-chocolate, 7up, iced-tea
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: electronic, salsa, punk, dubstep, house
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of punk##1
6. the fan of house is the person drinking iced-tea##1
7. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Beverage      | mirinda | hot-chocolate | cola | 7up | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | dubstep   | electronic       | salsa    | house   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
There 5 different types of food: orange, cherry, pear, banana, lettuce
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, scooter, helicopter, snowmobile, taxi
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person eating banana is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person eating orange is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person eating pear is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person eating cherry is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Food        | pear | banana | cherry | orange | lettuce |
| Transport   | scooter  | trike      | taxi | helicopter | snowmobile      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: rock-climbing, board-games, singing, puzzles, gardening
The people have 5 different jobs:  teacher, scientist, architect, firefighter, software-developer
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the scientist##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the scientist##1
3. the firefighter is on the right of the teacher##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the software-developer##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
6. the architect is on the far right##1
7. the software-developer is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Hobby   | puzzles    | rock-climbing        | singing | board-games | gardening |
| Job     | teacher | firefighter | software-developer  | scientist   | architect |

