.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
There 5 different types of food: blueberry, potato, cranberry, tomato, corn
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: sailing, climbing, water-polo, skateboarding, golf
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is the person eating corn##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is in the middle##1
5. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Food    | cranberry   | blueberry     | potato   | tomato         | corn |
| Sport   | sailing | skateboarding | water-polo | golf | climbing     |

