.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, cycling, snowboarding, rugby, rowing
The people use 5 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, scooter, tram, van
1. the person driving the tram is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
4. the person driving the scooter is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Sport       | rugby   | snowboarding   | cycling | rowing | lacrosse |
| Transport   | subway | scooter | tram   | van | snowmobile       |

