.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
5 different pets are kept: turtle, hamster, bird, fish, ferret
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, ice-hockey, climbing, lacrosse
1. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is in the middle##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Pet     | hamster   | bird  | ferret      | turtle | fish     |
| Sport   | climbing | ice-hockey | rowing | basketball   | lacrosse |

