.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, videographer, designer, fisherman, writer
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: surfing, cricket, baseball, rowing, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the writer##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the writer is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the dancer is on the right of the videographer##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Job     | videographer | dancer       | writer | fisherman | designer    |
| Sport   | rowing   | sailing | baseball  | cricket     | surfing |

