.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: video-games, reading, gardening, filmmaking, drawing
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: techno, folk, hip-hop, funk, r&b
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1
5. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of folk##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is the fan of folk##1
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | video-games | gardening | drawing | reading |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop       | funk   | r&b         | folk   | techno   |

