.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-10::.
There are 5 different nationalities: dutch, russian, thai, spanish, egyptian
5 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, chinchilla, rabbit, ferret, turtle
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the russian##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the thai##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is the dutch##1
4. the spanish is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the owner of the ferret is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
| Nationality   | egyptian | spanish | russian | thai | dutch |
| Pet           | turtle      | chinchilla    | ferret  | guinea-pig     | rabbit     |

