.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-11::.
There 5 different types of food: kiwi, nectarine, lettuce, onion, corn
5 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog, ferret, guinea-pig, rat
1. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is the person eating onion##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the person eating corn is on the far right##1
6. the person eating corn is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
7. the owner of the rat is the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
| Food   | onion | kiwi  | lettuce | nectarine | corn |
| Pet    | hedgehog    | guinea-pig | rat   | bird       | ferret        |

