.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-12::.
There 5 different types of food: peas, grapefruit, cauliflower, blueberry, radish
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rugby, skiing, parkour, tennis, volleyball
1. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person eating blueberry is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person eating radish is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Food    | peas | blueberry          | cauliflower    | radish | grapefruit  |
| Sport   | parkour  | volleyball | rugby | tennis | skiing |

