4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |      5      |
