.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: family, zombie, crime, martial-arts, superhero
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, snowboarding, basketball, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is basketball is in the middle##1
2. the person watching family movies is the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4      |    5     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie   | martial-arts  | family | superhero | crime  |
| Sport         | biathlon | snowboarding | basketball  | ice-hockey    | handball |

