.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, coffee, iced-tea, juice
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: biathlon, ice-hockey, parkour, golf, skiing
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage   | juice     | coffee       | almond-milk     | sprite  | iced-tea  |
| Sport      | golf | biathlon | ice-hockey | skiing | parkour |

