.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: horror, scientific, spy, western, time-travel
5 different pets are kept: turtle, cat, dog, horse, hedgehog
1. the owner of the cat is in the middle##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | time-travel | spy | horror | western |
| Pet           | hedgehog | horse  | cat    | turtle  | dog   |

 